# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This tool FETCHES third-party data (abstracts, citation metadata) into local
# files for your own analysis. Those build artifacts are NOT meant to be
# committed or redistributed — they aggregate copyrighted abstracts at scale and
# may contain credentials from any pages you saved. Keep them out of git.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

